    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. While the exterior paint retains a great luster, you may find a few minor stone chips or light scratches consistent with careful use. The interior is clean and smoke-free, though there is some very light bolster wear on the driver's seat. All major electronics and climate control systems are fully functional, offering a comfortable and worry-free driving experience.",
