      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard that warrants a definitive 'mint' designation. Every aspect of this vehicle, from its flawless exterior luster to the pristine condition of its interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled stewardship. This offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle in peerless, showroom-original condition. Engineering integrity and aesthetic perfection converge here to provide an unparalleled driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
