      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It's in absolutely perfect shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it's been kept in a garage its whole life. It\u2019s super clean inside and out. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a concours-level specimen featuring the legendary 4.0L S65 naturally aspirated V8. Engineered with eight individual throttle bodies and a 8,400 RPM redline, the powertrain remains in peak factory configuration with documented rod bearing prophylaxis. The chassis exhibits zero subframe fatigue, retaining its original rigidity and paired with a flawless Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system. The exterior features the weight-optimized carbon fiber roof in pristine condition, while the interior Novillo leather shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the purist",
      "price": 50000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service records included. Clean title.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Meticulously garage-kept and shielded from the elements, the original factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks or stone chips. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and matte, the buttons show zero wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting every fluid change and inspection. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every inch of this car reflects a lifetime of obsessive care. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and documented provenance, this is the finest example you will find on the market.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
