      "description": "We are proud to present an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, having been curated to the most exacting standards. The exterior finish retains its original luster, while the interior appointments remain pristine and free of wear. Mechanically, the vehicle delivers a driving experience synonymous with its factory-delivered state, supported by a comprehensive maintenance record. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a superlative example of the model, suited for the most sophisticated collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
